14 WHEREAS, additional charter school seats are needed to serve the 21,000 students who
15 currently appear on charter school wait lists in Georgia.
16 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
17 recognize February 26, 2025, as Charter Schools Day at the state capitol.
18 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
19 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia Charter
20 Schools Association, the public, and the press.
